Windows environment:
Install msys and mingw https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/files/
Install glut32 http://www.xmission.com/~nate/glut.html
Install ftgl https://sourceforge.net/projects/ftgl/develop
Install freetype2 http://www.freetype.org/index2.html

Set enviroment variables before starts eclipse: 

LIBRARY_PATH = C:\glut;C:\ftgl-2.1.3~rc5\msvc\build;C:\msys\1.0\local\lib;C:\freetype\lib

CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH =
C:\ftgl-2.1.3~rc5\src;C:\freetype\include;C:\msys\1.0\local\include;C:\glut;C:\freetype\include\freetype2;


PATH = C:\glut;C:\msys\1.0\local\bin;